\cf2 In this context, the goal of this work is to develop a 2D physics sandbox software, called Deskworld, for a multi-touch table. It is noted that the caracteristics inherent to a physics sandbox software fit perfectly the interface method choosen. That is because geometrical and free form drawing are most of the users' inputs.  \
